tafsir[3]{c,v,t}:
  18,100,"Men fenñinanay Jahannama yedduɓe ɓen fenñinngol ngol aldaa e jiɓayee fii yo ɓe seedo nge gite."
  18,102,"Enee ɓen yedduɓe Alla sikku ɓe waɗay jeyaaɓe Am ɓen immorde e Malaa'ikaaɓe e Nulaaɓe e Seytanuuji reweteeɓe gaanin Am?! Menen Men heblanii Jahannama fii yedduɓe ɓen galle fii werde maɓɓe."
  18,103,"Maaku -an Nulaaɗo-: \"Taw si men humpitay on -ko onon yo yimɓe- ɓurɗo mawnude yimɓe ɓen hayrere ka golle makko?"